## Coloring quoted text - coloring the first 7 levels:
color quoted color6 default
color quoted1 color3 default
color quoted2 color9 default
color quoted3 color2 default
color quoted4 color6 default
color quoted5 color3 default
color quoted6 color9 default
color quoted7 color2 default

